            >
            to Gaza, but was tightly controlled by the Israeli military. The
            visit was sharply criticized by Palestinians and aid workers, who
            saw it as a publicity stunt, not a genuine humanitarian inspection.
            That same day, 92 Palestinians were killed, including 51 while
            seeking aid.
          </p>
